values: Well, I am recording a CD for my solo project Memory's Fading on Saturday.  There should be twelve songs.  It will only be five dolluhs.  You should buy one.....or give me an i.o.u.  Anyway, let's hope it goes well.

Alright guys, maybe I will put something in here every now and then. I don't know what to say. Erm.....French Toast Crunch is my favorite cereal. Why you ask? Because it's friggin delicious. That's all I got. Want More?
